# The cbindgen-generated header is always written with LF. Pin it (and the
# source files whose toolchains emit LF) so a Windows checkout matches the
# committed bytes and `cargo build` does not rewrite line endings / cause churn.
include/screenbridge.h text eol=lf
*.rs    text eol=lf
*.swift text eol=lf
*.sh    text eol=lf
*.toml  text eol=lf
